WEBVTT

00:00.047 --> 00:02.674
Who's that? Who is that?

00:02.700 --> 00:04.902
Just a patient. Road traffic accident.

00:05.206 --> 00:07.131
We're only holding two cards, Stella.

00:07.251 --> 00:10.998
One, we have him two, we
have her and she's alive,

00:11.006 --> 00:13.349
the rest is a disaster.

00:13.349 --> 00:16.109
- Do you have a friend called Daisy?
- Why?

00:16.109 --> 00:17.942
There's something about her online,

00:18.149 --> 00:19.909
how she met Daddy one time.

00:19.909 --> 00:21.709
Am I being interviewed under caution?

00:21.829 --> 00:24.669
- Yes, you are.
- I knew that Rose was in that boot

00:24.789 --> 00:26.288
and I needed to get to her.

00:26.323 --> 00:28.341
And what about Mr Spector's life?

00:28.549 --> 00:30.829
Did you not have a duty to protect that?

00:32.988 --> 00:34.541
I need some help in here!

00:34.794 --> 00:35.953
Rose, what are you doing?

00:35.957 --> 00:37.333
- I want to go home.
- You can't.

00:37.364 --> 00:38.647
I want to go home!

00:38.722 --> 00:40.254
A man has come forward

00:40.272 --> 00:42.777
having seen Spector's
photograph on the news.

00:42.827 --> 00:44.725
He says Spector looks
like a man who rents

00:44.741 --> 00:46.756
a lock-up from him in East Belfast,

00:47.050 --> 00:48.909
under the name Baldwin.

00:49.029 --> 00:51.950
We've just landed a not
uninteresting little case.

00:52.117 --> 00:53.521
The Belfast Strangler.

00:53.641 --> 00:54.692
You stay away from him!

00:54.726 --> 00:56.568
I haven't been near him!
You need to get a grip!

00:56.579 --> 00:58.427
You're obsessed, it's pathetic!

00:58.793 --> 01:00.922
Who's pathetic now?!

01:00.955 --> 01:02.154
Ma'am.

01:03.763 --> 01:04.956
Hello, Daddy.

01:05.016 --> 01:06.498
It's me, Olivia.

01:06.726 --> 01:07.991
Why are you so big?

01:08.391 --> 01:11.387
And you, you look different, older.

01:11.712 --> 01:13.232
What's happening to me?

01:14.706 --> 01:15.982
More victims?

